- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper may involve the use of data structures and algorithms to study the computational complexity of CSPs. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper may have applications in AI, particularly in the area of constraint satisfaction and optimization.
